You can simply ask Alexa to control your “smart products”. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our “SV3CHome” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our “SV3CHome” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “SV3CHome” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “SV3CHome” skill, and you'll be navigated to “SV3CHome” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, lock the SV3CHome lock.
Alexa, unlock the SV3CHome lock.
Alexa, is the SV3CHome lock locked?
Alexa, is the SV3CHome lock unlocked?
Alexa, show me SV3CHome camera.
